Package com.camerontec.catalys.util.fast.codec

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IDecimalField
    Represents FAST decimalField element of template.
    IDictionary
    FAST dictionary.
    IDictionaryRegistry
    Registry of IDictionary objects, accessible by their name.
    IField
    A FAST scalar field - ie an integer, decimal, asciiString, etc.
    IName
    Name used to identify things in FAST.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DecimalField
    Decimal template elements are stored using StandardField unless the element has separate operators for exponent and/or mantissa, in which case it should be stored using this class.
    DictionaryRegistry
    Registry of named dictionaries.
    FastCodec
    The encoding and decoding are performed by four classes - this class, the CODEC, and a serializer/deserializer, the SERDES and the FastInputStream (decoding) or FastOuputStream (encoding).
    FastField  
    FastName  
    FastSerializerDeserializer  
    IntKeyDictionary
    FAST dictionary implementation which is designed for small positive int keys.

    Exception Description
    FastCodecException
